001package gbw.melange.common.builders;
002
003/**
004 * <p>IPartialBuilder interface.</p>
005 *
006 * @author GustavBW
007 * @version $Id: $Id
008 */
009public interface IPartialBuilder<T extends IBuilder<?>> {
010    /**
011     * Applies the sub-configuration to the parent builder, and returns the parent builder.
012     *
013     * @return a T object
014     */
015    T apply();
016}
